content.rendered:
Directed by Puri Jagannadh.

Written by Puri Jagannadh. Rishabh Purohit. A.R. Sreedhar. Kiran Thatavarthi.

Cast Nandamuri Balakrishna(Theda Singh). Shriya Saran(Sarika). Musskan Sethi(Harika). Vikramjeet Virk(Bob Marley). Kyra Dutt(ACP Kiranmayi) . Mohammad Ali((as Ali)). Joy Badlani(Mathur). Dhritiman Chatterjee(Jailor).Pavitra Lokesh. Prudhviraj(Prithvi Raj).Sairaj Suthari.Amit Tiwari.Temper Vamsi

Language Telugu.

Producers Rengarajan Jaiprakash. Dhimant Radia. Anne Ravi. Anand Prasad V..

Production Bhavya Creations. Goldmines Telefilms.
